{"id": 579, "genre": 1000, "title": "这些以“小”开头的流行语，你看烦了没？", "description": "这两年我讨厌的词基本全是“小”打头的，自称小透明就可以撒泼打滚，“你是大大嘛”，任何错事都扯一个“小字辈”给自己遮羞，这真是个美好的小时代啊，小百无禁忌，小就是理，都小习惯了，啥时候才能做一个大写的人啊？——@马伯庸", "record_count": 7892, "comment_count": 54, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160607194438kqHh57tpSQaoEcwI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-10-19T01:12:26Z", "questions": [{"id": 478, "title": "这些以“小”开头的流行语，你看烦了没？", "content": "这些以“小”开头的流行语，你看烦了没？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 17056, "content": "小透明", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193358al1SCjGfkd0EocMN.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17061, "content": "小时代", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193358jO7mUtP59i3e4Z8c.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17062, "content": "小鲜肉", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193358oOH2s7kNxBLYjlUC.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17063, "content": "小公举", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193358UeYTLqHZyS9lFEW3.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17079, "content": "小婊贝", "image": "img/option/option/201606071933590KwPmIj3RrSQTld4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17080, "content": "小清新", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193359xslOTyNR0VKmLktw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17081, "content": "小确幸", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193359KzQXAlkOoe98gaFV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17082, "content": "小苹果", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193359uL7ldWjXZk4Vi1b8.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 17083, "content": "小马甲（误", "image": "img/option/option/201606071934005bPAfoYvs93xK1Ip.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}